<ITM>(1) Are designated on an ENG Form 6282.</ITM><BRK/>
<BRK/>
<ITM>(2) Meet minimum training and experience requirements identified in <RID>EM 385-1-1</RID>, Chapter 2.</ITM><BRK/>
<BRK/>
<ITM>(3) Execute roles and responsibilities identified in <RID>EM 385-1-1</RID>, Chapter 2.</ITM><BRK/>
