<BRK/>
<TXT>Submit an IAQ Management Plan [within [15][_____] calendar days after<TAI OPT="DESIGN-BUILD"> design</TAI><TAI OPT="DESIGN-BID-BUILD">[ Contract award][ notice to proceed]</TAI>
 and not less than 10 calendar days before the preconstruction conference.][not less than 10 calendar days before 
the preconstruction conference.]  Revise and resubmit Plan as required by the Contracting Officer.  Make copies 
of the final plan available to all workers on site.  Include provisions in the Plan to meet the requirements 
